<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.238057>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Timea clandestina sp. nov. (MNRJ 18413 B, holotype). (A) Specimen after fixation; (B) Detail of a cross section showing the bouquets formed by tylostyles; (C) Cross section of specimen; (D) Tylostyles; (E) Variation of the spherostrongylasters to tylasters of the same category, including growth forms (gf); (F) Extremes of the variation in the same size category." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/238057/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

